  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: Al-Sharif al-Zahid Abu Muhammad al-Hasan ibn Hamza al-Alawi al-Husayni al-Tabari, may Allah have mercy on him, said: Abu Ja'far Muhammad ibn al-Hasan ibn al-Walid narrated to us, from Muhammad ibn al-Hasan al-Saffar, from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Isa, from Bakr ibn Salih, from al-Hasan ibn Ali, from Abdullah ibn Ibrahim, from Abu Abdillah al-Sadiq Ja'far ibn Muhammad, peace be upon them both, from his father, from his grandfather, peace be upon them, who said: The Messenger of Allah, peace be upon him and his progeny, said:",
    "ur": "فرمایا: مجھے الشریف الزاہد ابو محمد الحسن بن حمزہ العلوی الحسینی الطبری رحمہ اللہ نے خبر دی: رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وآلہ نے فرمایا:",
    "tr": "Eş-Şerîf ez-Zâhid Ebû Muhammed el-Hasen bin Hamza haber verdi: Resûlullah sallallahu aleyhi ve âlih buyurdu:",
    "fa": "شریف زاهد ابو محمد حسن بن حمزه خبر داد: رسول خدا صلی الله علیه وآله فرمود:",
    "id": "Al-Syarif al-Zahid Abu Muhammad al-Hasan bin Hamzah mengabarkan: Rasulullah shallallahu alaihi wa alihi bersabda:",
    "bn": "আল-শরীফ আল-যাহিদ আবু মুহাম্মাদ জানিয়েছেন: রাসূলুল্লাহ বলেছেন:",
    "es": "Al-Sharíf al-Záhid Abu Muhammad al-Hasan ibn Hamza informó: El Mensajero de Allah dijo:",
    "fr": "Al-Charîf al-Zâhid Abû Muhammad al-Hasan ibn Hamza a informé : Le Messager d’Allah a dit :",
    "de": "Al-Scharîf al-Zâhid Abu Muhammad al-Hasan ibn Hamza berichtete: Der Gesandte Allahs sprach:",
    "ru": "Аш-Шариф аз-Захид Абу Мухаммад аль-Хасан ибн Хамза сообщил: Посланник Аллаха сказал:",
    "zh": "尊贵的修行者阿布·穆罕默德·哈桑·本·哈姆扎告诉我：真主的使者说："
  }
}